/**
 * Activity feed — subagent tool blocks in chat history (Layer 2).
 * Extracted from orchestrator.ts during refactoring.
 * Design spec: ORCHESTRATION-UI-DESIGN.md → Layer 2: Subagent Tool Blocks
 *
 * Contains:
